<br />The best way to approach it is to do the easier way first, i.e., get a pre-made flash cart.  Learn how to use it, learn how it works, and learn its limitations.  Then start building your own custom cart from scratch.  That way you always have something that works to play with <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

